cd hello
nvim src/hello/main.cpp # or VS Code, or any clangd-enabled editor Add a vcpkg dependency: luban add fmt # edits vcpkg.json + regenerates luban.cmake
luban build # vcpkg auto-fetches fmt; rebuilds; updates compile_commands.json Add another target (separate exe / static lib in the same project): luban target add exe second-tool # creates src/second-tool/{CMakeLists.txt,main.cpp}
luban target add lib mycore # creates src/mycore/{CMakeLists.txt,*.cpp,*.h}

